use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533218\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2533218\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104vwm1665702725158.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vwm1665702725158.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/vwm1665702725158.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"vwm1665702725158\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      DB2 Connector Options\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__dbconnector_options_147683\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can assign connector options by setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$DB2_PARAMS</span> in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file. For all options, the default action is used by the connector, unless specifically overridden.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__topic_d48413e1_d48414e1_d48415e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48416e1_d48417e1_d48418e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$DB2_PARAMS</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n            n}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__topic_d31767e1_d31768e1_d31769e1_d31770e1_d31771e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d374119e74\">\n                        \n Options\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23840e1_d23841e1_d23842e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48422e1_d48423e1_d48424e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lca1665702725226.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lca1665702725226.html\" title=\"Enable or disable testing for the existence of tables and stored procedures.\">checks</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23843e1_d23844e1_d23845e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48425e1_d48426e1_d48427e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fug1665702705112.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fug1665702705112.html\" title=\"Set the default locking strategy employed by Uniface.\">default locking</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23846e1_d23847e1_d23848e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48428e1_d48429e1_d48430e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dqd1665702725479.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dqd1665702725479.html\" title=\"Specify the maximum size of field names.\">field name size</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23849e1_d23850e1_d23851e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48431e1_d48432e1_d48433e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mde1665702725613.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mde1665702725613.html\" title=\"Compatiblity option for Uniface 9.2, 9.3, or 9.4 (up to patch R107) to correctly align variable length fields.\">field alignment:4</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23852e1_d23853e1_d23854e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48434e1_d48435e1_d48436e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xti1665702725693.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xti1665702725693.html\" title=\"Specify whether statements remain open after a commit.\">hold statements</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23855e1_d23856e1_d23857e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48437e1_d48438e1_d48439e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vip1665702725886.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vip1665702725886.html\" title=\"Enable all characters to be used in an object or field, including diacritical signs.\">identifiers</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23858e1_d23859e1_d23860e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48440e1_d48441e1_d48442e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zmh1665702705308.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zmh1665702705308.html\" title=\"Set the isolation level for the database transactions of the connector.\">lock isolation</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23861e1_d23862e1_d23863e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48443e1_d48444e1_d48445e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xie1665702706126.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xie1665702706126.html\" title=\"Set the period a database operation will wait for a database lock to be released.\">maxlockwait</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23864e1_d23865e1_d23866e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48446e1_d48447e1_d48448e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lvk1665702674531.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lvk1665702674531.html\" title=\"Enable the use of the Graphic data type for double-byte-only storage\">nls</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23867e1_d23868e1_d23869e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48449e1_d48450e1_d48451e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qfw1665702726139.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qfw1665702726139.html\" title=\"Replace NULL values with default values.\">nulldefault</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23873e1_d23874e1_d23875e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48455e1_d48456e1_d48457e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cnt1665702726651.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cnt1665702726651.html\" title=\"Specify whether Uniface or the DBMS is responsible for maintaining referential integrity.\">ri</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23876e1_d23877e1_d23878e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48458e1_d48459e1_d48460e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pam1665702726925.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pam1665702726925.html\" title=\"Specify whether segmented fields will be stored to large object data types.\">segmented fields</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23879e1_d23880e1_d23881e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48461e1_d48462e1_d48463e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"exm1665702661663.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exm1665702661663.html\" title=\"Set the number of rows the connector selects from the DBMS in each step of the Uniface stepped hitlist.\">step size</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23882e1_d23883e1_d23884e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48464e1_d48465e1_d48466e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bdu1665702727695.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bdu1665702727695.html\" title=\"Sets the maximum size of table names in the database.\">table name size</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23885e1_d23886e1_d23887e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48467e1_d48468e1_d48469e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zxs1665702727948.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zxs1665702727948.html\" title=\"Enable or disable Unicode support.\">unicode</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23888e1_d23889e1_d23890e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48470e1_d48471e1_d48472e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"npx1665702705652.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/npx1665702705652.html\" title=\"Specify an isolation level to be used specifically by the lock ProcScript statement.\">update isolation</a>\n</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__topic_d31772e1_d31773e1_d31774e1_d31775e1_d31776e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d374119e296\">\n                        \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48476e1_d48477e1_d48478e1\">The syntax rules for <code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$DB2_PARAMS</code> are as follows:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23891e1_d23892e1_d23893e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48479e1_d48480e1_d48481e1\">Each assignment can be no longer than one line in the assignment file.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23894e1_d23895e1_d23896e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48482e1_d48483e1_d48484e1\">Each option may be specified only once.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23897e1_d23898e1_d23899e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48485e1_d48486e1_d48487e1\">Multiple options must be separated by a comma.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23900e1_d23901e1_d23902e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48488e1_d48489e1_d48490e1\">Parameter names and their values must be separated by a colon (<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>)</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23903e1_d23904e1_d23905e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48491e1_d48492e1_d48493e1\">The order in which the options are specified is not significant.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23906e1_d23907e1_d23908e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48494e1_d48495e1_d48496e1\">When a parameter name consists of more than one word, for example ‘segmented fields’, separate the words by exactly one space. Before or after the colon, an arbitrary number of spaces is allowed. For example:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48497e1_d48498e1_d48499e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$DB2_PARAMS = segmented fields : \n                             <code class=\"ph codeph\">enabled</code>\n</code>\n</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__li_d23909e1_d23910e1_d23911e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"vwm1665702725158__p_d48500e1_d48501e1_d48502e1\">Options are case-insensitive.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/msq1665702542189.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>[DRIVER_SETTINGS]</a><p>Use the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to specify the database and component engine connectors used, and their parameter options. The options available depend on the connector in use.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533218\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2533218\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "DB2 Connector Options Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 DB2 Connector Options You can assign connector options by setting USYS$DB2_PARAMS in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file. For all options, the default action is used by the connector, unless specifically overridden. USYS$DB2_PARAMS Option { , Option n} Options checks default locking field name size field alignment:4 hold statements identifiers lock isolation maxlockwait nls nulldefault ri segmented fields step size table name size unicode update isolation Description The syntax rules for USYS$DB2_PARAMS are as follows: Each assignment can be no longer than one line in the assignment file. Each option may be specified only once. Multiple options must be separated by a comma. Parameter names and their values must be separated by a colon ( : ) The order in which the options are specified is not significant. When a parameter name consists of more than one word, for example ‘segmented fields’, separate the words by exactly one space. Before or after the colon, an arbitrary number of spaces is allowed. For example: USYS$DB2_PARAMS = segmented fields : enabled Options are case-insensitive. Related Links [DRIVER_SETTINGS] Use the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to specify the database and component engine connectors used, and their parameter options. The options available depend on the connector in use. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}